1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,225
=Episode 14=

3
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:55,979
Chen, have some water and take a break.

4
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,079
You've already made

5
00:00:57,399 --> 00:00:58,399
a lot of progress.

6
00:00:58,760 --> 00:00:59,640
It's still not enough.

7
00:01:00,662 --> 00:01:03,150
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

8
00:01:03,237 --> 00:01:06,990
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

9
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:12,079
Keep your back straight.
Hold your horse stance steady.

10
00:01:13,660 --> 00:01:16,280
Practice your stance for three years
before learning anything else.

11
00:01:17,519 --> 00:01:20,040
If you want to learn to fight,
start with the horse stance.

12
00:01:21,825 --> 00:01:24,837
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

13
00:01:25,037 --> 00:01:28,087
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

14
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:31,162
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

15
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:34,587
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

16
00:01:34,812 --> 00:01:38,562
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

17
00:01:38,562 --> 00:01:41,425
♪I belong to no one♪

18
00:01:41,487 --> 00:01:44,937
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

19
00:01:44,937 --> 00:01:47,975
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

20
00:01:47,975 --> 00:01:54,300
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪

21
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,480
Is this... the legendary

22
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,680
Gale-Breaking Thirteen Strikes?

23
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:02,560
Is that really its name?

24
00:02:02,925 --> 00:02:03,565
That's right.

25
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,840
When I was young,

26
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:08,159
I once saw my master's master's master
practice it.

27
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:09,319
Chen,

28
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:09,959
no.

29
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:13,319
By seniority, you should actually
be my Martial Uncle.

30
00:02:13,799 --> 00:02:14,360
Martial Uncle.

31
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:16,159
Please allow me to pay my respect.

32
00:02:17,300 --> 00:02:18,199
Mr. Hong, please rise.

33
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,879
Thank you for helping me.

34
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:23,479
No, no.

35
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:25,199
Martial Uncle,

36
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:27,159
with skills like yours,

37
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:29,262
Qin Aoxue will be easy to deal with.

38
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,520
No problem at all.

39
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,439
The layout is square,

40
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,651
the arrangement orderly.

41
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:47,830
It's sheltered from wind and rich in qi.
It has excellent feng shui.

42
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:50,439
Excellent feng shui.

43
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:52,000
Master,

44
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,199
may I ask.

45
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:53,919
Where does

46
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,719
the evil force
that's blocking my fortune come from?

47
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,199
Let me take a look.

48
00:02:59,360 --> 00:02:59,840
Alright.

49
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:10,960
Aoxue,

50
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,159
this is Master Yu from Xuanji Hall.

51
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:13,759
Come here.

52
00:03:16,220 --> 00:03:18,280
My sister's trained too much
she's a little... off.

53
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:20,039
Please don't mind her.

54
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:24,199
Why would I lower myself
to be bothered with someone dense?

55
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:25,719
Exactly.

56
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:26,479
However...

57
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,560
martial artists are fierce by nature.

58
00:03:30,370 --> 00:03:31,560
Her eyes carry killing intent,

59
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,510
and the aura
of violence crowns her head.

60
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,875
I'm afraid she's the one

61
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:37,719
hindering your fortune.

62
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:39,960
Master,

63
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:41,360
is there a way to break it?

64
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:42,240
Definitely.

65
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:43,439
I have here

66
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:46,879
a wolf fang from the Three Kingdoms era.

67
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:49,080
With my spiritual blessing added,

68
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,479
it will protect you
and turn your fortune around.

69
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:53,240
Thank you, Master.

70
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,039
Master,

71
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,199
if it truly works,

72
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:04,562
there will be a generous reward.

73
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,174
Mr. Qin, you're here too?

74
00:04:30,279 --> 00:04:31,000
Hello, Mr. Qin.

75
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,560
Miss Qin,

76
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,600
for my sake,

77
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:35,800
please go easy

78
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,399
later on, alright?

79
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,439
Sorry, Master Hong.

80
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,199
I never throw a fight.

81
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:41,720
No, I mean...

82
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:43,160
I'm worried about you.

83
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,279
No head-butting.

84
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:51,279
No elbow strikes.

85
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:52,639
No striking the groin.

86
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,920
No striking the back of the head.

87
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:54,839
Understood?

88
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:59,000
Come on!

89
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,720
Round one,

90
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:01,199
begin!

91
00:05:02,625 --> 00:05:04,337
(Show your spirit. Go beyond yourself.
Competition is more than victory.)

92
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:12,160
Referee, look at him!

93
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,399
Sorry.

94
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:14,490
I only enforce the rules.

95
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,399
Do you have any professionalism at all?

96
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:31,600
Ye Chen, turn around and face me!

97
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,399
I never attack from behind.

98
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,399
Turn around? Where's my pride
if I just obey you?

99
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,590
Are you going to follow the rules or not?

100
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,800
The referee isn't even here.

101
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,990
What rules are there to follow?

102
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,759
Ye Chen, if you didn't want
to fight me properly,

103
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:45,120
why did you accept the challenge?

104
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,759
Alright, come on.

105
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,790
Let's fight properly.

106
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,160
Your words.

107
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:02,680
Round two,

108
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,439
begin!

109
00:06:06,550 --> 00:06:08,000
Ye Chen, are you even a man?

110
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,990
Are you going to fight or not?

111
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,360
Get off the stage! Get off!

112
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,120
Why are you running? Come back here!

113
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,519
Get off!

114
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:23,319
Come back!

115
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,199
Get down!

116
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,639
Just come down!

117
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,279
Mind your manners!

118
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:29,639
What are you doing?

119
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:33,680
Ye Chen.

120
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:35,619
Ye Chen.

121
00:06:35,975 --> 00:06:37,087
Can you stop fooling around?

122
00:06:37,662 --> 00:06:39,129
I just want a proper fight with you.

123
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,279
I am fighting you properly.

124
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:43,690
Look, I'm already sweating all over.

125
00:06:43,775 --> 00:06:44,175
No,

126
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,240
Miss Qin,

127
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:46,839
don't worry.

128
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,150
I've had about enough fun.

129
00:06:49,439 --> 00:06:50,120
Next round,

130
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,600
we'll fight properly.

131
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,879
Your word?

132
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,990
A promise is a promise.

133
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:58,462
Mr. Qin, the real show is about to start.

134
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,040
Come on!

135
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,759
Go!

136
00:07:16,759 --> 00:07:17,399
Come on!

137
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:18,290
That's more like it!

138
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,040
Come!

139
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:28,560
Come on!

140
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,319
Let's go!

141
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,439
Come on!

142
00:07:31,079 --> 00:07:31,639
Come on!

143
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,360
Hit him!

144
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,319
Go on!

145
00:07:33,519 --> 00:07:34,319
Come on!

146
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,199
You're here.

147
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,800
Come on!

148
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,000
Go on!

149
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:47,759
Come on!

150
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,990
What does he mean by that?

151
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:04,959
That was impressive.

152
00:08:20,260 --> 00:08:21,800
Ye Chen kept dodging and playing tricks,

153
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,790
and that still counts as a win?

154
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,335
Shut up!

155
00:08:26,625 --> 00:08:27,264
I lost.

156
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:29,160
Miss Qin, you're a good sport.

157
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:50,240
Are you alright?

158
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:51,840
I'm fine.

159
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,320
Good.

160
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,200
Wait here for a moment.

161
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:10,559
Ye Chen,

162
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:12,919
you tricked me.

163
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:14,120
Yes.

164
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,400
I just wanted to tell you.

165
00:09:17,837 --> 00:09:19,370
Even if you're Qin Gang,

166
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:20,637
I'll make you pay

167
00:09:20,925 --> 00:09:22,440
if you cross me.

168
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:24,039
I already told you,

169
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,399
Madam Li's death wasn't my doing.

170
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:30,440
Stop pestering me from now on.

171
00:09:33,125 --> 00:09:34,120
Well, sorry about that.

172
00:09:34,730 --> 00:09:36,559
Right now,
you're still the biggest suspect.

173
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,550
You not only had a motive,

174
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:39,720
you also have a record.

175
00:09:39,730 --> 00:09:41,660
So if I don't suspect you,
who should I suspect then?

176
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:42,240
You...

177
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,480
Fine.

178
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,240
If that's what you want to think,

179
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,039
there's nothing I can do.

180
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:54,039
But let me tell you this today.

181
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,559
If there's a problem,

182
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,120
come at me.

183
00:09:58,519 --> 00:10:00,159
Stay away from Aoxue.

184
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:04,480
Hey.

185
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,320
I suggest you take
your precious daughter

186
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,900
to the hospital for a proper check-up.

187
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,279
What do you mean?

188
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:14,080
She's sick.

189
00:10:15,879 --> 00:10:17,200
You're the one who's sick!

190
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,080
Aoxue!

191
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,960
Mr. Quan once taught me

192
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:33,370
the four diagnostic methods
of traditional medicine.

193
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:35,159
The first is inspection.

194
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:37,360
Observe the vitality, the complexion,

195
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,279
and the body.

196
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:40,720
The vital energy of the organs

197
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,240
is reflected in the eyes.

198
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,879
The whites of Qin Aoxue's eyes
are flushed red,

199
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,120
and her pupils are dilated.

200
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:47,840
It's a sign of her inner heat
disturbing the mind,

201
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:49,360
with stagnant qi and blood.

202
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,200
This isn't an ordinary illness.

203
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,559
She's poisoned.

204
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:54,559
Poisoned?

205
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,399
You mean someone poisoned Aoxue?

206
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:58,720
That's very possible.

207
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:01,879
What kind of poison is it?

208
00:11:01,879 --> 00:11:02,837
We're not sure yet.

209
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:05,000
Further tests and analysis are needed.

210
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,480
Is there any treatment?

211
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,840
For now, there's no targeted treatment.

212
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,890
We can only use
some conventional medicine

213
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,090
to stabilize her condition
and slow the deterioration.

214
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:15,080
What's the worst-case scenario?

215
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,200
She could fall

216
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:18,360
into a coma,

217
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:19,399
become paralyzed,

218
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:22,080
or even face a life-threatening condition.

219
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,840
Who would poison Qin Aoxue?

220
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,279
I'll have Dongxue investigate further.

221
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,120
But no matter who did it,

222
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:32,799
Qin Gang

223
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:35,720
will probably believe
that it's you who did it.

224
00:11:37,862 --> 00:11:39,022
He can come if he wants.

225
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:40,679
From what I know,

226
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:43,639
Qin Gang treasures his daughter the most.

227
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:46,620
I think we should go with the flow.
Use this opportunity

228
00:11:46,620 --> 00:11:48,400
to force him
to hand over the prescription.

229
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:49,840
This is your chance.

230
00:12:13,824 --> 00:12:16,312
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

231
00:12:16,399 --> 00:12:20,152
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

232
00:12:20,612 --> 00:12:25,549
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

233
00:12:25,712 --> 00:12:27,999
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

234
00:12:28,312 --> 00:12:30,992
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

235
00:12:32,062 --> 00:12:34,687
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

236
00:12:34,987 --> 00:12:37,999
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

237
00:12:38,199 --> 00:12:41,249
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

238
00:12:41,362 --> 00:12:44,324
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

239
00:12:44,592 --> 00:12:47,749
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

240
00:12:47,974 --> 00:12:51,724
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

241
00:12:51,724 --> 00:12:54,587
♪I belong to no one♪

242
00:12:54,649 --> 00:12:58,099
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

243
00:12:58,099 --> 00:13:00,774
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

244
00:13:00,774 --> 00:13:07,112
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
